    3DVIA helps consumers make the best buying decisions by providing the 3DEXPERIENCE® in a rich and engaging online environment

    3DVIA provides enterprises and consumers, smart 3D space planning solutions that enable new ways to engage, consider, and make the best choice.

    For enterprises, 3DVIA Home offers home improvement retailers and brand manufacturers a cloud-based, omnichannel space planning solution to engage consumers, generate high quality sales leads, and shorten sales cycle. With 3DVIA Store, retailers test and optimize store design concepts result is a better in-store consumer experience and results. For individuals, 3DVIA enables consumers to design and plan home projects in a social way. Consumers can find inspiration from thousands of other projects, build their own concepts or simply visualize ideas quickly using dedicated room configurators.

    • 3D Space Planning for Consumers

      Imagine, Design & Share Your 3D Housing Projects

      For consumers, HomeByMe is an online 3D space planning service to Imagine, Design and Share 3D housing projects. With HomeByMe, you will create your entire home in 3D and experiment with thousands of products and textures before sharing your projects with friends and experts.

       Explore the discipline

    • 3D Space Planning for Enterprise Consumers

      Generate High-quality Leads, Increase Revenue and Delight Customers

      For enterprise consumers, 3DVIA Home provides home improvement retailers and brand manufacturers a smart 3D space planning solutions, hosted on the cloud. Omnichannel, easy to use and automated, 3DVIA Home increases your lead flow, shortens your sales cycle and delights your customers.

       Explore the discipline

    • 3D Space Planning for Stores

      Accelerate Your Store Updates & Enhance Your Visual Merchandising Performance

      For retail stores and store chains, 3DVIA Store provides a collaborative 3D space planning solution to share concepts and drive change. 3DVIA Store helps you adapt a design or merchandising plan to local store constraints resulting in better store compliance and profitability and a better in-store experience for your customers
